          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蔡瑁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张允",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张允。"
        },
        {
          "character": "毛阶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "毛阶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "于禁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张郃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众位将军请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "文聘、许褚、张辽、蔡瑁、张允、毛阶、于禁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张郃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相自得襄阳，众军皆有封赏，今又齐集我等，必有南征之意。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鼓响。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张郃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鼓角声高，丞相升帐，你我两厢伺候。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四文堂、四大铠引曹操同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丹书铁卷，拥旌旄、扫烟尘，群雄尽灭；汉室天子如木偶，锦华夷不日曹接。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张郃、文聘、许褚、张辽、蔡瑁、张允、毛阶、于禁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见丞相。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "站立两厢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张郃、文聘、许褚、张辽、蔡瑁、张允、毛阶、于禁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "盖世乾坤已破，一心想占山河。斩杀不待蹉跎，献帝孙刘在佐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫，姓曹名操字孟德。沛国谯郡人也，骁骑出身。自起义兵破黄巾，诛董卓、\n擒吕布、灭袁术、平袁绍、得荆襄，称汉家丞相。前者刘备在当阳被老夫一\n战，兵败夏口，恐结连东吴是滋蔓也。今奏奉天子命诏，统领八十三万人马大\n下江南，孙权必惊疑而来降，吾事济矣。\n张郃听令：命汝以为旱路先锋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张郃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文聘听令：命汝以为水路先锋。蔡瑁、张允以为水军头领，余下之将，随营调\n遣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "文聘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传令下去，我军水陆并进，船骑双行，沿江而走，八十三万人马，大下江南。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张郃、文聘",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。\n令出。唗！下面听者：丞相有令，我军水陆并进，船骑双行，沿江而走，八十\n三万人马大下江南。"
        },
        {
          "character": "许褚、张辽、蔡瑁、张允、毛阶、于禁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张郃、文聘",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传令毕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就此起马。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。张郃、文聘、许褚、张辽、蔡瑁、张允、毛阶、于禁同领下，伞夫随曹操同下。）"
        }
      ],
