    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "众人",
        "刘备",
        "吾东吴文共武兵精粮有",
        "待等到冬至后大功成就",
        "曹孟德兵扎在三江夏口",
        "糜芳",
        "诸葛亮",
        "鲁肃"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四文堂、刘备同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汉室苗裔，图大业，复立帝基。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "邑郡生英俊，飘然自不群。创业心攸重，求贤礼志勤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤，姓刘名备字玄德。乃大树娄桑人氏，本中山靖王之后，孝景帝之玄孙，倚\n附堂兄刘表，不幸晏驾。孺子刘琮懦弱无为，将荆襄九郡献与曹瞒，使我弃新\n野、走樊城、败当阳、走夏口，无处栖身。只得退守江夏。哎！正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张牙舞爪潜波底，怎得风云起卧龙。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（糜芳上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "糜芳",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晓日貔貅帐，春风虎豹营。"
        },
        {
          "character": "糜芳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启主公：东吴鲁肃过江求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！我想鲁肃与孤素无相识，他今到此，必有要事。请诸葛先生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "糜芳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请诸葛先生！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（诸葛亮上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "纬地经天安排策，人称南阳大丈夫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢座。唤山人进帐，有何军情事议？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "适才糜芳报道，东吴鲁肃过江求见，不知何故？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那曹操统率八十三万人马，虎踞江汉。他焉不差人探听虚实。他今此来，正和\n我意，待他若问之时，主公只推不知，待山人全凭三寸不烂之舌，去往江东，\n激动孙权，与曹操南北相争，山人在于中取事，占得汉室诸土。此乃天赐之机\n会也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生高见。请暂退。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告退。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（诸葛亮下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来！有请鲁大夫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "糜芳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请鲁大夫！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（糜芳下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗯哼！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鲁肃上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金殿礼决坐，江山一帆风。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！刘皇叔！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鲁大夫过江来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫请来上坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不敢不敢。肃乃一介儒生，焉敢与皇叔对坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你乃江东贵客，理应上坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这就不敢，旁侍一坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鲁大夫车马降临，蓬荜生辉，实切可幸。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "久闻皇叔大名，无缘拜会；今幸得相见，实为欣慰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢岂敢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "近闻皇叔与曹会战，必知彼军虚实。敢问皇叔，那曹军约有几何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "备兵微将寡，但闻曹军一至，备便急走，不知彼军虚实。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闻得皇叔用诸葛孔明之谋，两次火烧得曹操亡魂丧胆，何言不知也？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "除非问诸葛先生，便知其详。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孔明安在？愿求一见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，请诸葛先生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请诸葛先生进帐！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（诸葛亮上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "江东无决计，来使探虚实。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见过鲁大夫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，鲁大夫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不敢。君莫非是卧龙公？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不敢。草字孔明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "久仰久仰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢岂敢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "向慕先生先生才德，未得拜晤；今幸相遇，愿领大教。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亮才疏学浅，有辱明闻。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问先生：曹兵共有多少？可下江南否？⑴"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曹操奸计，亮已尽知；但恨力未及，故且避之，以待天时耳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皇叔今将止于此否？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我主与苍梧太守吴臣，乃旧日故交，将往投之。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吴臣那里，兵微粮少，自不能保，焉能容人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吴臣那里，虽不能久居，且暂依之，别有良图。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎！我主孙仲谋，虎踞江东，兵精粮足，又极敬贤礼士；今为君计，莫若遣一\n心腹往结江东，同心破曹，以图大事，岂不美哉？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我主与孙将军素不相识，恐虚费说词。况且，别无心腹之人可使差矣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生令兄，现为东吴参谋，日望与先生相见。肃不才，愿与同见我主，共议大\n事，你看如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，孔明乃是吾之师，顷刻不可相离，安可去也？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，自今孙刘两家结好，同心破曹，以图大事。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主公，事已至此，山人只得请命一往。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生须要早回。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晓得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "孤与你朝夕间不离左右，\n到江东必须要早早回头。\n我兵微将又寡孤心担忧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹孟德兵扎在三江夏口、鲁肃",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "孙仲谋素平生待人忠厚，\n敬贤才礼能士一礼所求；\n管教你报却那当阳之仇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吾东吴文共武兵精粮有、诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主公！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吾东吴文共武兵精粮有、诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我今同鲁子敬往柴桑郡口，\n致使那曹兵将必一旦休。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吾东吴文共武兵精粮有、诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "待等到冬至后大功成就、鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皇叔，我们告辞了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鲁肃下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "那时节保主公驾坐荆州。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（诸葛亮下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "恨曹瞒逼孤穹看看束手，\n天赐下鲁子敬凑我机谋。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
